xhwicap_clb_ff.h File Reference

Detailed Description

This header file contains bit information about the CLB FF resource. This header file can be used with the XHwIcap_GetClbBits() and XHwIcap_SetClbBits() functions.

Define Documentation

#define XHI_CLB_XQ   0
 

Index into the CONTENTS and SRMODE for XQ Register.

#define XHI_CLB_YQ   1
 

Index into the CONTENTS and SRMODE for YQ Register.

Variable Documentation

const XHwIcap_ClbFf XHI_CLB_FF
 

This structure defines the bits associated with a Flip Flop in a CLB tile. Note that there are 8 FFs, the XQ and YQ Registers in Slice 0, 1, 2 and 3.
